{"tid":2503110,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"《無常》- 你我若有緣，上窮碧落下不過黃泉（10）(堅完)","createTime":"2021-04-24T19:11:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-26T13:10:31.000Z","uid":78726,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7933bdaf6448f4094907e7d183b4ee2a276eca3a","tid":2503110,"uid":78726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-24T19:11:55.000Z","msg":"多少廝守，轉身一別已是千年。<br />\n<br />\n多少往事，在旁人眼中，本該苦得巴不得忘清，但當事人卻甘之如飴地記著。<br />\n<br />\n多少痴人，脫了凡胎毅然入鬼籍，不惜用上永恆的時間去等待，圖的也無他；<br />\n<br />\n求的，不過相見而已。<br />\n<br />\n----------------------------------------------<br />\nPost 1:<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/264273/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/264273/page/1</a><br />\nPost 2:<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/316462/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/316462/page/1</a><br />\nPost 3:<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/389964/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/389964/page/1</a><br />\nPost 4:<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/459467/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/459467/page/1</a><br />\nPost 5:<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/550459/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/550459/page/1</a><br />\nPost 6:<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/665241/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/665241/page/1</a><br />\nPost 7:<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/745461/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/745461/page/1</a><br />\nPost 8:<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/908708/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/908708/page/1</a><br />\nPost 9:<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1916231/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1916231/page/1</a><br />\nPost 10:<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2458878/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2458878/page/1</a><b